"zu-top-search-input" id="q" name="q" autocomplete="off" value="" maxlength="100" placeholder="搜索你感兴趣的内容…"><button type="submit" class="zu-top-search-button"><span class="hide-text">搜索</span><span class="sprite-global-icon-magnifier-dark"></span></button></form></div><div id="zg-top-nav" class="zu-top-nav"><ul class="zu-top-nav-ul zg-clear"><li class="zu-top-nav-li " id="zh-top-nav-home"><a class="zu-top-nav-link" href="/" id="zh-top-link-home" data-za-c="view_home" data-za-a="visit_home" data-za-l="top_navigation_home">首页</a></li><li class="top-nav-topic-selector zu-top-nav-li " id="zh-top-nav-topic"><a class="zu-top-nav-link" href="/topic" id="top-nav-dd-topic">话题</a></li><li class="zu-top-nav-li " id="zh-top-nav-explore"><a class="zu-top-nav-link" href="/explore">发现</a></li></ul><div class="zu-top-nav-live zu-noti7-popup zg-r5px no-hovercard" id="zh-top-nav-live-new" role="popup" tabindex="0"><div class="zu-top-nav-live-inner zg-r5px"><div class="zu-top-live-icon">&nbsp;</div><div class="zu-home-noti-inner" id="zh-top-nav-live-new-inner"><div class="zm-noti7-popup-tab-container clearfix" tabindex="0"><button class="zm-noti7-popup-tab-item message"><span class="icon">消息</span></button><button class="zm-noti7-popup-tab-item user"><span class="icon">用户</span></button><button class="zm-noti7-popup-tab-item thanks"><span class="icon">赞同和感谢</span></button></div></div><div class="zm-noti7-frame-border top"></div><div class="zm-noti7-frame"><div class="zm-noti7-content message"><div class="zm-noti7-content-inner"><div class="zm-noti7-content-body"><div class="zm-noti7-popup-loading"><span class="noti-spinner-loading"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="zm-noti7-content user" style="display:none;"><div class="zm-noti7-content-inner"><div class="zm-noti7-content-body"><div class="zm-noti7-popup-loading"><span class="noti-spinner-loading"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="zm-noti7-content thanks" style="display:none;"><div class="zm-noti7-content-inner"><div class="zm-noti7-content-body"><div class="zm-noti7-popup-loading"><span class="noti-spinner-loading"></span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="zm-noti7-frame-border bottom"></div><div class="zm-noti7-popup-footer"><a href="/notifications" class="zm-noti7-popup-footer-all zg-right">查看全部 &raquo;</a><a href="/settings/notification" class="zm-noti7-popup-footer-set" title="通知设置" ><i class="zg-icon zg-icon-settings"></i></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="zu-global-notify" id="zh-global-message" style="display:none"><div class="zg-wrap"><div class="zu-global-nitify-inner"><a class="zu-global-notify-close" href="javascript:;" title="关闭" name="close">x</a><span class="zu-global-notify-icon"></span><span class="zu-global-notify-msg"></span></div></div></div><main class="pure-g receptacle"><section class="page-content-main pure-u-1 pure-u-md-17-24"><div class="unit-inner"><div class="module roundtable-profile clearfix"><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018" class="photo visible-desktop"><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-823d5358a5ae386a0147cac32a9966d4_xl.jpg" srcset="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-823d5358a5ae386a0147cac32a9966d4_b.jpg 2x" alt="2018 诺贝尔奖巡礼" class="avatar"></a><div class="content"><div class="title"><h1><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018">2018 诺贝尔奖巡礼</a></h1><span class="status">已结束</span></div><div class="description">举世瞩目的诺贝尔奖声名远播，业已成为自然科学、经济学和文学等领域的最高奖项，2018 年评选结果将于 10 月 1 日起陆续揭晓。知乎「诺贝尔奖巡礼」系列圆桌也已迎来第四个年头。今年我们再度携手中国科普博览，邀请各学科的专家学者，老时间、老地点，和大家一起畅谈诺奖、畅游科学。</div><div class="actions"><button class="button-link share pull-left" data-id="288" data-token="nobel2018"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button><span class="visits text-muted">50283728 次浏览 </span><span class="bull">&bull;</span><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/followers" class="followers text-muted"><span class="count" data-count="14431"> 14431</span> 人关注</a></div></div></div><div class="module"><ul class="menu-nav horizontal"><li ><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018">134 <span class="nowrap">条动态</span></a></li><li ><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/questions">81 <span class="nowrap">个问题</span></a></li><li ><a href="/roundtable/nobel2018/comments">32 <span class="nowrap">条讨论</span></a></li></ul></div><div class="feeds loose user-answers"><ul class="items" data-paging><li class="item" data-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-113230850"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/287833877/answer/457393851"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="26240192"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="287833877"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="113230850"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="457393851"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/287833877/answer/457393851">有哪些物理学上的事实，没有一定物理学知识的人不会相信？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>3355</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">3355</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/jiehou1993" data-hovercard='p$t$jiehou1993'>小侯飞氘</a>，<span title="专业研究飞氘" class="bio">专业研究飞氘</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="小侯飞氘" data-entry-url="/question/287833877/answer/457393851"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">世上没有不透风的墙。哪怕你用纯金属浇铸一堵严丝合缝的墙，气体原子（特别是氢）在量子隧穿效应的作用下，也有一定概率“瞬移”到墙的另一边去。最近在文献上看到氢原子的超级扩散（superdiffusion)，算是比较反经典直觉的一种现象，这里正好给大家介绍一…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/287833877/answer/457393851">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="3355"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/lin-si-xiang-86" data-hovercard='p$t$lin-si-xiang-86'>林果</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/he-guo-bing-43" data-hovercard='p$t$he-guo-bing-43'>方的河</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/mu-zi-yun-zhi-86" data-hovercard='p$t$mu-zi-yun-zhi-86'>佟佳斡啜</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>世上没有不透风的墙。</p><p>哪怕你用纯金属浇铸一堵严丝合缝的墙，气体原子（特别是氢）在量子隧穿效应的作用下，也有一定概率“瞬移”到墙的另一边去。</p><hr><p>最近在文献上看到氢原子的超级扩散（superdiffusion)，算是比较反经典直觉的一种现象，这里正好给大家介绍一下。</p><p>为了照顾普通读者，我且把“氢原子的超级扩散”这个现象拆分成几个小问题，并尽量用通俗的语言来回答。</p><ul><li><b>先来一道送分题，什么是扩散？</b></li></ul><p>这个概念大家应该比较熟悉。你把一滴墨水滴入水缸中，墨水最终会均匀的分布至整个水缸。这中物质自发从高浓度区域向低浓度区域的转移的过程，就称为扩散。</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-d25770c80d8109437a01714e6057ed47_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="281" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-d25770c80d8109437a01714e6057ed47_r.jpg"><figcaption>墨水在水中的扩散</figcaption></figure><p><br></p><ul><li><b>再来一题热身题，扩散的本质是什么？</b></li></ul><p>大家应该知道，我们感受到的温度其实是微观分子热运动的表现，这种热运动是随机且无规则的。正是这种随机的热运动驱动着染料分子到处乱跑，从而充满整个水缸。</p><p>这就好比下课铃一响，一群好动的熊孩子便会离开教室各种疯，不一会儿操场上就到处都是熊孩子的身影了。</p><p><br></p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-173953b450318884f726b28ec2bb726a_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="288" data-rawheight="216" class="content_image" width="288"><figcaption>氢原子在金属表面的随机扩散</figcaption></figure><p><br></p><ul><li><b>大题来了，什么是超级扩散？</b></li></ul><p>很多情况下，一个原子的扩散需要挤开周围的其他原子，这需要一定的能量：</p><p><br></p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-73b0acf8ed071f6d67e3f810fa036927_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="324" data-rawheight="216" class="content_image" width="324"><figcaption>扩散过程中的能量变化（右侧曲线）</figcaption></figure><p><br></p><p>越过这个能垒需要的能量是由热运动提供的。当温度较高时，激烈的热运动能轻易提供这个能量，扩散自然就快。反过来，温度低，没有足够的热动能，扩散也就越困难。</p><p>如果我们测量不同温度下的扩散速率，会发现随着温度的下降，扩散速率呈指数式降低，也就是下图中的红色虚线（注意纵坐标是对数尺度）：</p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-5cc46743db330493a0f80aa49f7ba588_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1148" data-rawheight="717" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-672f0abe337baefa74f98206bdb280d7_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1148" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-5cc46743db330493a0f80aa49f7ba588_r.jpg"><figcaption>氢、氘在铜表面的扩散系数随温度变化</figcaption></figure><p>可以看到，氘的扩散速率确实是指数式降低，算是正常扩散。</p><p>然而作为氘的同位素，氢和氘化学性质几乎完全一致，按理说扩散行为也应该区别也不大，但氢的扩散速率却降到一定程度就不变了。</p><p>这种低温下速率异常高的扩散，就称为超级扩散。</p><ul><li><b>压轴题，为什么氢会出现超级扩散？</b></li></ul><p>如果把上面提到的扩散能垒看成一堵墙，能量不够的话，一般情况下就越不过这堵墙。但是（敲黑板），说了多少次了，答大题不能想当然，要揣摩出题人意思知道么。“一般情况下不能”，潜台词就是说“特殊情况下可以”，而氢就是这种特殊情况。</p><p>氢作为质量最小的原子，具有很强的量子效应。这意味着，氢原子的平均能量虽然是一个守恒值，但在短时间内具有很大的不确定性。</p><p>通过这种能量-时间不确定性，氢原子有一定概率“无中生有”的提高自己的能量，从而越过扩散能垒这堵墙：</p><p><br></p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-666636eac09c2beefdc88a89b75069bd_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="700" data-rawheight="393" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="700" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-666636eac09c2beefdc88a89b75069bd_r.jpg"><figcaption>隧穿效应：经典力学中由于能量不足无法穿过的能垒墙，在量子力学中有一定概率穿过</figcaption></figure><p>而这种量子效应是和温度无关的。在低温下，尽管热运动不足以驱动氢原子扩散时，但量子效应依然能驱动扩散，甚至占据扩散的主导地位。因此扩散速率不随温度降低而降低。</p><p>另一方面，量子效应随质量增长迅速衰弱。而氘原子质量是氢原子的两倍，这也解释了为什么氘原子没有明显的超级扩散效应。</p><p><br></p><p>欢迎关注：</p><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/collection/229588890" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" class="internal">认真写科普</a></script><a class="time" href="/question/287833877/answer/457393851">2018-08-01</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>3355</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="26240192"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">286 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-report"><i class="fi fi-report"></i>举报</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic4.zhimg.com/1eb9b8c7e7ddc53f26db62a3ecd99dd7_m.jpg"><meta name="own" content="true"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="action-item js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></li><li class="hidden-phone item-collapse js-collapse"><button class="button-text"><i class="sprite-global-icon-fold-round-default"></i>收起</button></li><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop phone-actions"><button class="button-text menubutton"><i class="fi fi-3-dot"></i>更多</button><div class="menu goog-menu goog-menu-vertical zh-answer-more-actions" style="display:none"><div class="goog-menuitem js-share">分享</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-collect">收藏</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-thank ">感谢</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-report">举报</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic4.zhimg.com/1eb9b8c7e7ddc53f26db62a3ecd99dd7_m.jpg"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></div></div></li></ul></div></li><li class="item" data-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-120251656"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/295288932/answer/496005796"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="27896752"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="295288932"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="120251656"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="496005796"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/295288932/answer/496005796">历年的诺贝尔化学奖有哪些给了物理学家？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>187</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">187</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/jiehou1993" data-hovercard='p$t$jiehou1993'>小侯飞氘</a>，<span title="专业研究飞氘" class="bio">专业研究飞氘</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="小侯飞氘" data-entry-url="/question/295288932/answer/496005796"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">不得不说说计算物理学界几乎无人不知的<a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Walter_Kohn" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Walter Kohn</a>。Kohn因创建密度泛函理论（Density Functional Theory, DFT），极大的降低了量子力学计算的计算量，使得精确模拟化学反应成为可能。Kohn虽然因此获1998年诺贝尔化学奖，但他本人却是个如假包换的理论物理…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/295288932/answer/496005796">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="187"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/leonard-18-72-57" data-hovercard='p$t$leonard-18-72-57'>Leonardio</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/ji-guang-zhi-ao-luo-la" data-hovercard='p$t$ji-guang-zhi-ao-luo-la'>极光之奥罗拉</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/lu-jia-xin-49-90" data-hovercard='p$t$lu-jia-xin-49-90'>七谷</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>不得不说说计算物理学界几乎无人不知的<a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Walter_Kohn" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Walter Kohn</a>。</p><p>Kohn因创建密度泛函理论（Density Functional Theory, DFT），极大的降低了量子力学计算的计算量，使得精确模拟化学反应成为可能。</p><p>Kohn虽然因此获1998年诺贝尔化学奖，但他本人却是个如假包换的理论物理学家。</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-7c7cb650f2cffc03a58089eb49f9427a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="220" data-rawheight="298" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-78a6f0cc96b33a5b5deb56588bc3e2c2_b.jpg" class="content_image" width="220"><figcaption>2012年89岁的Walter Kohn</figcaption></figure><p>要解释Kohn的贡献，还得从量子力学说起。</p><p>自从薛定谔方程被提出来之后，物理学家们很快便用它计算了氢和氦的光谱等基本化学性质，发现与实验数据高度吻合。</p><p>理论上，薛定谔方程能够准确的预言所有物质的化学性质。因此，另一位量子力学奠基人狄拉克便优越感爆棚了，忍不住开了个全图嘲讽，大意为：“化学这个学科已经被我们物理学家终结了。你说你们花那么多钱鼓捣那些个瓶瓶罐罐有啥用？我们一根笔一张纸算算就把反应结果算出来了。”</p><p>然后没过多久，狄拉克就喜闻乐见的被打脸了。</p><p>没错，理论上用薛定谔方程是能算出所有的化学反应过程。但是，这个方程是真*宇宙无敌超级*难解。随着电子个数的增加，解薛定谔方程的计算量可以说是爆炸式的增长。</p><p>一个含N个电子具有3N个自由度，求解其薛定谔方程，计算量M正比于：</p><p><img src="//www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=M+%5Cpropto+p%5E%7B3N%7D%2C+%5C+3%5Cleq+p%5Cleq10" alt="M \propto p^{3N}, \ 3\leq p\leq10" eeimg="1"></p><p>如果解一个氢原子（一个电子）的薛定谔方程需要1微秒，也就是百万分之一秒。</p><p>那么，在最理想的情况（p=3）下，解碳原子（6个电子）需要10分钟。</p><p>氧原子（8电子）需要两天。</p><p>钠原子（11电子）需要127年。</p><p>氯原子（17电子）需要500亿年。</p><p>......</p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a9e7aa04d7aea7fc7f0c1e1717ba5bb2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="453" data-rawheight="346" data-size="normal" data-caption="" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9f5a297a13868812ce3ec79fdd7b1d46_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="453" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a9e7aa04d7aea7fc7f0c1e1717ba5bb2_r.jpg"></figure><p>求解原子序数20以上的薛定谔方程几乎是不可能的，这种迅速增长的计算量也被称为指数墙——一堵压根无法越过的墙。</p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-03036fc203f7fd58944d3ff2fe4b3951_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="508" data-rawheight="414" data-size="normal" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4c4a292f7d4bb7f50510b676bf1f926d_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="508" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-03036fc203f7fd58944d3ff2fe4b3951_r.jpg"><figcaption>随电子个数的增长，求解多体薛定谔方程的计算量指数式升高，也称指数墙</figcaption></figure><p>于是Kohn就琢磨着，既然翻不过去，干脆把墙推倒算了，</p><p>薛定谔方程之所以这么难解，是因为它把所有电子的波函数都单独考虑，而N个电子就有3N个自由度。</p><p>而Kohn证明，用不着弄清楚每个电子的精确波函数，只需要知道电子的空间密度分布就能描述整个体系了。这就好比称一袋米的重量时，用不着把每个米粒都称一遍然后加起来。</p><p>通过把体系用电子密度来描述，N个电子的波函数就被当成了一个函数来处理，3N个自由度也就缩减到了xyz这3个自由度，计算量一下就降下来了。</p><p>借助Kohn发展的密度泛函理论，以前只能算算一两个原子的计算量，现在可以模拟近千个原子，普通的化学反应基本上都能处理。这一方法也成了计算化学、材料、物理学界最常用的一种计算方法之一。</p><hr><p>相关阅读：</p><a data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" href="https://www.zhihu.com/collection/229588890" class="internal">认真写科普</a><p></p></script><a class="time" href="/question/295288932/answer/496005796">2018-09-21</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>187</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="27896752"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">13 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-report"><i class="fi fi-report"></i>举报</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="0"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic4.zhimg.com/1eb9b8c7e7ddc53f26db62a3ecd99dd7_m.jpg"><meta name="own" content="true"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-6" target="_blank" class="action-item js-copyright">禁止转载</a></li><li class="hidden-phone item-collapse js-collapse"><button class="button-text"><i class="sprite-global-icon-fold-round-default"></i>收起</button></li><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop phone-actions"><button class="button-text menubutton"><i class="fi fi-3-dot"></i>更多</button><div class="menu goog-menu goog-menu-vertical zh-answer-more-actions" style="display:none"><div class="goog-menuitem js-share">分享</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-collect">收藏</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-thank ">感谢</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-report">举报</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="0"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic4.zhimg.com/1eb9b8c7e7ddc53f26db62a3ecd99dd7_m.jpg"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-6" target="_blank" class="js-copyright">禁止转载</a></div></div></li></ul></div></li><li class="item" data-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-113555084"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/288033186/answer/459175560"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="26284195"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="288033186"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="113555084"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="459175560"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/288033186/answer/459175560">有哪些化学上的事实，没有一定化学知识的人不会相信？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>780</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">780</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/jiehou1993" data-hovercard='p$t$jiehou1993'>小侯飞氘</a>，<span title="专业研究飞氘" class="bio">专业研究飞氘</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="小侯飞氘" data-entry-url="/question/288033186/answer/459175560"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand">受力状态会影响化学反应的进行。例如正常情况下，氢不溶于铁，溶解过程吸热。但是如果你把铁用力拉伸，使得铁原子间的距离增大，氢就能更容易跑到铁原子的间隙中去，从而把氢的溶解过程变成放热。正是基于这个原理，导致把一根金属弯曲后丢到酸中后，拉伸区…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/288033186/answer/459175560">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="780"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/wo-you-yi-hu-jiu-82" data-hovercard='p$t$wo-you-yi-hu-jiu-82'>我有一壶酒</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/mo-ying-pa" data-hovercard='p$t$mo-ying-pa'>末影帕</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/xie-mei-86" data-hovercard='p$t$xie-mei-86'>叶玫</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>受力状态会影响化学反应的进行。</p><p>例如正常情况下，氢不溶于铁，溶解过程吸热。</p><p>但是如果你把铁用力拉伸，使得铁原子间的距离增大，氢就能更容易跑到铁原子的间隙中去，从而把氢的溶解过程变成放热。</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-32ccf6a75774adf50480ce7944d6ae0b_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="540" data-rawheight="413" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-04b2bffc3b146d409c4ff870621eb202_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="540" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-32ccf6a75774adf50480ce7944d6ae0b_r.jpg"><figcaption>氢在铁中的溶解能随应变的变化</figcaption></figure><p>正是基于这个原理，导致把一根金属弯曲后丢到酸中后，拉伸区域的金属腐蚀速度比压缩区域要快很多。这个现象被称为应力腐蚀。</p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-f60a8f6c5cd60320d626aea4b37faaf9_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="510" data-rawheight="270" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-f2ffc0d431bf1b43758310216a87baf7_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="510" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-f60a8f6c5cd60320d626aea4b37faaf9_r.jpg"><figcaption>金属的应力腐蚀：外侧金属受到拉力，因此更容易被腐蚀开裂</figcaption></figure><p><br></p><p>欢迎关注：</p><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/collection/229588890" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" class="internal">认真写科普</a><p></p></script><a class="time" href="/question/288033186/answer/459175560">2018-08-03</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>780</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="26284195"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">65 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-report"><i class="fi fi-report"></i>举报</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic4.zhimg.com/1eb9b8c7e7ddc53f26db62a3ecd99dd7_m.jpg"><meta name="own" content="true"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="action-item js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></li><li class="hidden-phone item-collapse js-collapse"><button class="button-text"><i class="sprite-global-icon-fold-round-default"></i>收起</button></li><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop phone-actions"><button class="button-text menubutton"><i class="fi fi-3-dot"></i>更多</button><div class="menu goog-menu goog-menu-vertical zh-answer-more-actions" style="display:none"><div class="goog-menuitem js-share">分享</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-collect">收藏</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-thank ">感谢</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem js-report">举报</div><div class="goog-menuseparator"></div><div class="goog-menuitem"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="1"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic4.zhimg.com/1eb9b8c7e7ddc53f26db62a3ecd99dd7_m.jpg"><a href="/terms#sec-licence-1" target="_blank" class="js-copyright">作者保留权利</a></div></div></li></ul></div></li><li class="item" data-type="Answer"><a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-120712459"></a><link itemprop="url" href="/question/294997722/answer/498539473"><meta itemprop="question-id" content="27832050"><meta itemprop="question-url-token" content="294997722"><meta itemprop="answer-id" content="120712459"><meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="498539473"><div class="item-header"><h2 class="item-title"><a class="js-title-link" target="_blank" href="/question/294997722/answer/498539473">诺贝尔化学奖的研究成果给我们的社会带来了哪些影响？</a></h2></div><article class="entry answer"><div class="entry-left hidden-phone"><a class="rating hidden-expanded js-expand js-vote-count" data-bind-votecount>60</a><div class="votebar visible-expanded"><button class="up " title="赞同"><i class="fi-voteup-arrow"></i><span class="count">60</span><span class="sr-only">赞同</span></button><button class="down" title="反对，不会显示你的姓名"><i class="fi-votedown-arrow"></i><span class="sr-only">反对，不会显示你的姓名</span></button></div></div><div class="entry-body"><div class="entry-meta"><strong class="author-line"><a class="author" href="/people/jiehou1993" data-hovercard='p$t$jiehou1993'>小侯飞氘</a>，<span title="专业研究飞氘" class="bio">专业研究飞氘</span></strong></div><div class="entry-content js-collapse-body" data-author-name="小侯飞氘" data-entry-url="/question/294997722/answer/498539473"><div class="summary hidden-expanded js-expand"><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harold_Urey" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Harold Urey</a>，因发现了氢的同位素氘获1934年诺贝尔化学奖。氘（deuterium，D），也称重氢或氢-2，名字来源于希腊语的“第二（deuteros）”，其原子核由一个质子和一个中子构成，是氢的稳定同位素，广泛分布在海水中。尽管氘在核磁共振、化学示踪、制药等领…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/294997722/answer/498539473">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="60"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/measoundhear" data-hovercard='p$t$measoundhear'>measoundhear</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/zhen-zhen-miao-miao-41" data-hovercard='p$t$zhen-zhen-miao-miao-41'>真真喵喵</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/shu-yu-jing-er-feng-bu-zhi-10-9" data-hovercard='p$t$shu-yu-jing-er-feng-bu-zhi-10-9'>知音世所希</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harold_Urey" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Harold Urey</a>，因发现了氢的同位素氘获1934年诺贝尔化学奖。</p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8b6a397d299a10ce3fae1585868a7dfb_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="220" data-rawheight="311" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4da9967543ce8c23f7bff86606ff2156_b.jpg" class="content_image" width="220"><figcaption>Harold Urey</figcaption></figure><p>氘（deuterium，D），也称重氢或氢-2，名字来源于希腊语的“第二（deuteros）”，其原子核由一个质子和一个中子构成，是氢的稳定同位素，广泛分布在海水中。</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-94e9c3d1ee691fc6f898091b6f5c03d3_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="571" data-rawheight="338" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-27cc5685b7a8c8c075f8a8540fed4277_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="571" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-94e9c3d1ee691fc6f898091b6f5c03d3_r.jpg"><figcaption>氢的三种同位素，氕（protium）氘（deuterium）和氚（tritium）</figcaption></figure><p>尽管氘在核磁共振、化学示踪、制药等领域都有很重要应用，但说到氘，很多人首先想到的应用，恐怕还是核能发电。</p><hr><p><b>裂变堆</b>中很多常见的核燃料，例如铀235，只能与速度较慢的中子碰撞发生裂变反应。但链式反应中产出的中子往往是快中子，需要进行减速才能维持反应的进行。由于氘和中子的碰撞截面较大，能有效的对中子进行减速。因此，氘的氧化物重水经常被用作裂变反应堆中的慢化剂，同时也扮演冷却剂的角色推动发电机发电。</p><p>常见的重水反应堆一般都是加拿大设计的CANDU（Canada Deuterium Uranium）技术，我国的秦山核电站就采用了这种技术。目前全球总共有超过44座CANDU及CANDU衍生型核电站。</p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-940a441f98ec2de2a30fa183a35fbdc0_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1800" data-rawheight="1080" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9e8d42b8e4b6aeb3bf0dd490df8b6127_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1800" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-940a441f98ec2de2a30fa183a35fbdc0_r.jpg"><figcaption>CANDU型重水反应堆</figcaption></figure><p><b>聚变堆</b>中氘扮演着更重要的角色。从困难程度来看，最容易发生的三个核聚变反应，全部都需要用氘作为燃料。</p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7eb549712ee9dcaba29355f225ac5c62_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="894" data-rawheight="144" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="894" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7eb549712ee9dcaba29355f225ac5c62_r.jpg"><figcaption>核聚变反应按反应截面（困难程度）排序</figcaption></figure><p>最重要的是，氘在地球上的储实在是太太太丰富了，在海水中平均每6420个氢中就能找到一个氘。全部拿来当聚变燃料的话，这些氘足以让人类以目前的能源消耗速度使用亿年以上（2012年的全球年耗能约 <img src="//www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=5.8%5Ctimes10%5E%7B20%7D+J" alt="5.8\times10^{20} J" eeimg="1"> ）。因此核聚变被认为能够“一劳永逸”的解决人类的能源问题。</p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f6cd2457665b79bdf58618726d893f29_b.jpg" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="350" data-default-watermark-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-99b0fd750baf9eb5a57247b04a35411d_b.jpg" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f6cd2457665b79bdf58618726d893f29_r.jpg"><figcaption>中科院等离子体所的东方超环核聚变研究装置，俗称“小太阳”</figcaption></figure><p>另外，由于恒星的能源也是核聚变，因此我们研究聚变的经常戏称自己是"种zhong太mo阳gu"的：</p><blockquote>啦啦啦种太阳<br>啦啦啦种太阳<br>啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦<br>种太阳<br>到那个时候世界每一个角落<br>都会变得都会变得温暖又明亮</blockquote><hr><p>欢迎关注：</p><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/collection/229588890" data-draft-node="block" data-draft-type="link-card" class="internal">认真写科普</a><p></p></script><a class="time" href="/question/294997722/answer/498539473">2018-09-26</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>60</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="27832050"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">6 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-collect"><i class="fi fi-fav"></i>收藏</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-report"><i class="fi fi-report"></i>举报</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><meta name="copyrightStatus" content="2"><meta name="disableCopyAvatar" content="https://pic4.zhimg.com/1eb9b8c7e7ddc53f26db62a3ecd99dd7_m.jpg"><meta name="own" content="true"><a href="/copyright/apply?answer=498539473" target="_blank" class="action-item js-copyright">申请转载</a></li><li class="hidden-phone item-collapse js-collaps